message.body: @rockytopterror Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE

message.body: @VillaJack Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE AFTER
